title: Tim Smith, Christina Lauer win Ironman Maryland
text:
Published By: Baltimore Sun: Outdoors - Today 
Tim Smith of Brooklyn, N.Y., and Christina Lauer of Arlington, Va., won top honors at the Ironman Maryland triathlon Saturday in Cambridge. ...
